{"tid":1386932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果真係入晒動暴罪 會否出現巴士底監獄","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T04:54:40.000Z","uid":9813,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5a92993c566b8b0e101978c458cd6d7129e826","tid":1386932,"uid":9813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e9b990f7a02961045f90e7e8e64cb4781faee1","tid":1386932,"uid":9813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:23:39.000Z","msg":"希望各位能夠平安無事就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8725148a659b5dfaaa1ac17300141876bf02ec","tid":1386932,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"認真問 咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514333528a137a24e8a863c7023892ef177375e0","tid":1386932,"uid":289262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae8725148a659b5dfaaa1ac17300141876bf02ec","tid":1386932,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"認真問 咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"它建造於14世紀，當時是一座軍事城堡，目的是防禦百年戰爭英國人的進攻，所以就建在巴黎城門前。後來，在巴黎市區不斷擴大下，巴士底監獄要塞成了市區東部的建築，失去了防禦外敵的作用。18世紀末，它是控制巴黎的制高點，自亨利四世後，法國國王在裡面駐紮了大量軍隊。監獄專門關押政治犯，例如文學家伏爾泰便曾在此處坐牢，因此不少當時的民眾視巴士底監獄是法國王權專制獨裁的象徵之一。<br />\n<br />\n19世紀的浪漫主義歷史學家把巴士底監獄當作法國專制王朝的象徵，並把1789年7月14日巴士底監獄被人民佔領的事件描繪成偉大的功績，代表英勇的巴黎人民解放被壓迫的農民的一次革命勝利。自從1879年，為了紀念法蘭西第一共和國的建立，法國政府宣布把7月14日定為國慶節。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%95%E7%8B%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%258B%25B1&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCubTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=c487ea27\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%95%E7%8B%B1</a>"},{"pid":"22ee89fc04f9b46d47b3bbca5a5622d8a01c1c5d","tid":1386932,"uid":20522,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"ae8725148a659b5dfaaa1ac17300141876bf02ec","tid":1386932,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"認真問 咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:26:24.000Z","msg":"乜依家中二歷史科搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8a77eb1507db0ba5a3ea9cf4cc3b5e940758e9","tid":1386932,"uid":263751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd5a92993c566b8b0e101978c458cd6d7129e826","tid":1386932,"uid":9813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"到依加仲未醒覺既話<br />\n可以約埋47後集中營見"},{"pid":"963bc316fda4f31542f2fca4a53e79d5bd91194c","tid":1386932,"uid":9813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d8a77eb1507db0ba5a3ea9cf4cc3b5e940758e9","tid":1386932,"uid":263751,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd5a92993c566b8b0e101978c458cd6d7129e826","tid":1386932,"uid":9813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"到依加仲未醒覺既話<br />\n可以約埋47後集中營見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"唔洗等到47了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi